  "state_prompts": [
    "## State: START\n- **Description:** Navigate to Coosa Valley Tech CrowdFiber page\n- **Triggers:**\n\t1. If it is on the chrome homescreen\n- **Actions:**\n\t1. Go to https://connect.coosavalleytech.com/front_end word for word\n\t2. TERMINATE AT THIS POINT",
